item.title: I need help changing home coords
item.dc:creator: @SheppehSays SheppehSays
item.description:
@SheppehSays wrote:

[quote=“flipmc, post:4, topic:255680”]It could be in client.java, but it has to be in player.java
Trying making a new account, and then stay where you are. Then make like a command like, ::coords and then search for those coords. If not, then your server might be using Misc.Random, meaning it teleports you to different places within a specific coordinate.

Example:

Teleport(3208 + Misc.random(10), 3422 + Misc.random(3), 0, 1);[/quote]

Omg… Can’t you read???You just said what he said, I need to change the teleport, Not where you start, The teleport…
